name: Chikkumz
description:
2D space shooter made with Godot Engine for Godot Wild Jam in which you try to save humanity from egg aliens.

I accidentally introduced a bug at the last second with a typo that prevented the victory screen from triggering after you beat the game. It's supposed to take you to a screen that reads:

YOU WIN!

THANK YOU FOR SAVING US ALL CAPTAIN STARDANK!
